OL,3,CProlific fare dodger spared jail term
OL,4,Cover 112 unpaid train tickets
OL,6,FOne of Britain's most prolific train
OL,7,Ffare dodgers has been spared jail over
OL,8,F112 convictions for not paying for a
OL,9,Fticket on journeys spanning nearly two
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FCharles Brohiri, 29, did not pay fares
OL,13,Fvalued at more than #3,000 for Govia
OL,14,FThameslink Railway (GTR) train
OL,15,Fjourneys between February 2024 and
OL,16,FNovember last year.
