OL,3,CProlific fare dodger spared jail term
OL,4,Cover 112 unpaid train tickets
OL,6,FThe defendant, originally from
OL,7,FHatfield in Hertfordshire, but who has
OL,8,Fbeen homeless for years, pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to 76 charges of failing to pay
OL,10,Ffor a rail ticket, and was convicted
OL,11,Fin his absence in August 2024 of a
OL,12,Ffurther 36 charges.
OL,14,FAt his sentencing hearing at
OL,15,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,16,FWednesday, district judge Nina Tempia
OL,17,Falso took into consideration a further
OL,18,F16 offences ` with three of that
OL,19,Fnumber said to have been committed on
OL,20,FTuesday.
