OL,4,Cover 112 unpaid train tickets
OL,6,F"Be under no illusion if you commit
OL,7,Fany other offences and you do not
OL,8,Fcomply with the requirement on this
OL,9,Forder you will be back in court," the
OL,10,Fjudge warned him.
OL,12,FThe court was told Brohiri continued
OL,13,Fhis campaign of fare dodging after
OL,14,Fbeing banned last April from entering
OL,15,FThameslink stations as part of his
OL,16,Fbail conditions.
OL,18,FHis offending is said to have
OL,19,Fcontinued unabated, with the last
OL,20,Fallegation of fare dodging recorded
OL,21,Fone day ago ` on February 10 this year.
