OL,6,F"With the exception of the period of
OL,7,FOctober, November (and) December 2024,
OL,8,Fthere have been offences in every
OL,9,Fmonth since February 2024 to the
OL,10,Fpresent day," prosecutor Lyndon Harris
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FEleanor Curzon, defending, told the
OL,14,Fcourt: "He has expressed remorse and
OL,15,Fregret for having continued to travel
OL,16,Fon the trains during the whole period
OL,17,Fand particularly the period when he
OL,18,Fhas been appearing before you judge."
